Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就讓那個孩子覺醒為神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.49,0:00:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊時間準備儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前你母親和你的力量曾救過我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算拼上性命也要救出你的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.50,0:00:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你銘記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想離開這裡 去見那個叫姆伽羅的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.26,0:00:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去見姆伽羅妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事想見面確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.47,0:00:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 請幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德·達克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掃平惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神之護佑與我同在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊就交給你們幾個了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,團長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 還不能劇烈活動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個惡魔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我跟狄亞思解決掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不需要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪我沒救下她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法接受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我始終不認為那人配當奧爾良騎士團的團長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從一隻受傷的惡魔手上拯救人民都辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種人當團長我無法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別那麼灰心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也是上面決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們根本改變不了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計上面人喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是美女團長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 團長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒把握好輕重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來換我當你對手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年前 我殺害了神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了聖女應有的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此深重的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便獻上我的生命也償還不清吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 我依然想以騎士的身份活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去的罪行沒能挽救的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無力的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要背負這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃避很容易
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我還不想放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在被解除團長一職前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:07:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望盡全力當好奧爾良騎士團的團長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會追隨你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神都不在就要繼位嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前所未聞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣行得通嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是新的亞納提王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏利歐斯17世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在此宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類畏懼惡魔 崇拜神明的時代必將結束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在此向大家保證
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會創造出人類盛世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下還望三思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何要進攻眾神殿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為對創造人類盛世有幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很確定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人與神長久以來的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然要以這種方式斷絕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些東西必須要弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可神卻拒絕交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此就只能搶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下所指的東西是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯聽命於我 就告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個國家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今仍有跟你一樣崇拜神明的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 只要原聖女肯聽命於我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必那幫人也會放棄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選吧 貞德·達克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是聽命於我 共創人類盛世呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是離開王都呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 後面就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選吧 貞德·達克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米迦勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 屋子不會被吹跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個...很難說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我名叫貞德·達克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我兒子 艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德·達克啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說她偷偷住在郊外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可實在沒想到她有孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 竟然擁有能令漆黑兵無力化的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不是跟人類生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子要是到神手上就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經封堵了她的逃跑路線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將她逼向王都了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住她應該只是時間問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論生死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要別讓她把孩子交給神就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒收穫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定把她逼到這附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面的命令 找到就立刻殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分三路行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要殺我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們去那邊找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 看那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去裡面找
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現就立即殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要活下去 艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論今後遇上多麼痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必定會有人向你伸出援手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要相信那人 一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我很快就被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.15,0:22:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今都不知道阿爾的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:22:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德 你受苦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.53,0:23:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽羅妹妹肯定就是艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這樣一來就不是姆伽羅妹妹就成男的了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想見艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.00,0:23:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 還想跟他一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這肯定是米迦勒大人的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米迦勒大人？誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾的父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 我想見見那個叫姆伽羅的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越獄是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這監獄島越獄的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今還沒出現過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽見沒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我們要開創先河了 貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.95,0:23:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 貞貞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.95,0:23:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是阿薩禿頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是禿頭 是謝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 謝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.70,0:23:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 下回 神擊的巴哈姆特Virgin Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.92,0:23:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼定了 謝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.96,0:24:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫阿薩謝爾 這很重要
